Foundation Button Pack
================================

This is a button pack for the Zurb Foundation framework, it adds 13 new buttons in this version including:

* warning
* facebook
* twitter
* instagram
* tumblr
* flickr
* pinterest
* linkedin
* skype
* dropbox
* google plus
* path
* github


Using the pack
-------------------------

Simply add a reference to the buttons.css file and then add the required class to your button or link.

E.g. : <a class='button facebook' href='#'>Facebook</a>


Examples
-------------------------

All the buttons are in use in the demo folder or view them live on: http://www.ryanmcdonough.co.uk/labs/foundation/buttons/index.html
